    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed the required level for MRL 2. Six factors are not assessed, consistent with MRL 2 requirements for a Class II device with medium model influence. Validation results demonstrate NIH prediction within 8% of experimental measurements across all five operating points, with RH < 1 satisfied at all conditions including the identified worst-case point. The CFD model is judged credible for its intended use of identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the CPB device.",
